cast.overview: Predestination chronicles the life of a Temporal Agent sent on an intricate series of time-travel journeys designed to prevent future killers from committing their crimes. Now, on his final assignment, the Agent must stop the one criminal that has eluded him throughout time and prevent a devastating attack in which thousands of lives will be lost.
cast.title: Predestination

details.biography: Represented by Gilchrist Management, Sophie Cusworth is a 19 year old Melbourne based actor, with a playing age of 14 - 18. Her latest credits include the lead role of Sam in ABC's comedy series It's A Date, and a bit part role in the latest Spierig Brothers film, Predestination. Sophie recently graduated from the Victorian College of the Arts' Actors Studio, and studies a Bachelor of Arts at The University of Melbourne.  - IMDb Mini Biography By: Sophie Cusworth
details.name: Sophie Cusworth
